70
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:19,920
- No, not chili. - No, this is for you.

71
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:22,160
- Can I have the green pepper? - Here's your green pepper.

72
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:24,120
- We have everything. - Can we eat this?

73
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,480
- Go over there. - It's for you.

74
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,959
- Here you go. - Shi Yi.

75
00:08:27,319 --> 00:08:28,800
Come on over!

76
