The pack of hungry wolves will finish the food.

77
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,759
Come on. Hurry.

78
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:34,559
- I can't eat this much. - Eat up.

79
00:08:34,559 --> 00:08:36,120
Mr. Lan, you look so handsome when you grill meat.

80
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:37,240
