93
00:08:58,330 --> 00:09:00,330
He's jealous of me now because he can't perform.

94
00:09:01,210 --> 00:09:02,399
I'm jealous of you?

95
00:09:02,519 --> 00:09:04,330
You were the one who always complained...

96
00:09:04,330 --> 00:09:07,360
