176
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,080
We were about to sign the contract.

177
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:07,000
But something urgent came up and I had to leave.

178
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,240
He told me to send the project to his email.

179
00:13:09,919 --> 00:13:11,519
Did you make any changes afterward?

180
00:13:11,519 --> 00:13:13,200
If you did, what did you change?

181
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:16,320
I actually made some very basic improvements.

182
00:13:16,759 --> 00:13:19,320
I increased the overall sense of chaos...

183
00:13:19,759 --> 00:13:22,919
